      • launchGen

        @PostMapping(value="/Go")
public java.lang.String launchGen(@RequestParam(name="entityList")
                                                             java.lang.String entityList,
                                                             @RequestParam(name="basePackage")
                                                             java.lang.String basePackage,
                                                             @RequestParam(name="outputDir")
                                                             java.lang.String outputDir,
                                                             @RequestParam(name="component")
                                                             java.lang.String[] components)
        Calls GenJavaComponents.launch() with instructions received from web user
        Parameters:
        entityList: - List of data model entities for which to generate code.
        basePackage: - Name of base application package under which all sub-packages and generated classes shall reside
        outputDir: - Output file directory, typically "output" under the root of the RADSpringBootGen app.
        components: - List (array) of components to generate for each of the entities: Service interface, Service implementation class, (web) Controller class, and/or Edit.html.
        Returns:
        Name of landing html file.
